txt.en: 'Have you heard that crazy girl on the commons? Ranting about pies or some such thing.'
'Something needs to be done about the shrews around here, they've been digging up my garden again!'
'Mayor Whitfoot had best mind his step, or next election he'll find himself out on his duff.'
'Those hobbits in Little Delving think quite a bit of themselves. They look at us like we're from Waymeet!'
